with cte_operation_id_station as(
SELECT DISTINCT PART_ID, STATION_NMB FROM PRODUCTION_PARTS_OPERATIONS
WHERE ID IN
(SELECT DISTINCT OPERATION_ID FROM PRODUCTION_BATCHES_OPERATIONS
WHERE BATCH_ID IN
(SELECT DISTINCT ID FROM PRODUCTION_BATCHES
WHERE BATCH_NUMBER = '%s')))

SELECT PRODUCTION_PARTS.ID, PRODUCTION_PARTS.CREATION_TIME, PRODUCTION_PARTS.PART_SERIAL, PRODUCTION_PARTS.LAST_STATION_NMB, PRODUCTION_PARTS.LAST_STATUS, PRODUCTION_PINIONS.PINION_SERIAL, DOCK_AUDIT_BATCHES.BATCH_CODE, cte_operation_id_station.STATION_NMB
FROM cte_operation_id_station, PRODUCTION_PARTS 
left join PRODUCTION_PINIONS on PRODUCTION_PARTS.PINION_ID = PRODUCTION_PINIONS.ID
left join DOCK_AUDIT_BATCHES on PRODUCTION_PARTS.BATCH_ID = DOCK_AUDIT_BATCHES.ID

ORDER BY CREATION_TIME

with cte_users (usr_id, usr_name)
AS
(
select ID, [USER_NAME] from USER_DATA
	UNION
	select ID, [USER_NAME] from USER_DATA_HISTORY
)
select 
ID, CREATION_TIME, STATION_NMB, OPERATION_STATUS, cte_users.usr_name
from PRODUCTION_PARTS_OPERATIONS
left join cte_users on [USER_ID] = cte_users.usr_id
where (PART_ID = '%s' AND STATION_NMB <> 30) OR (PART_ID = '%s' AND STATION_NMB = 30)
order by ID
